## 9. Common Mistakes & Key Takeaways

| # | Takeaway |
|---|----------|
| 1 | **Multilingual embeddings** enable one KB for all languages |
| 2 | **LLM answer generation** provides natural translation |
| 3 | **Similarity thresholds** prevent bad matches |
| 4 | **This pattern scales** to 50+ languages |

